                <h1>Board of Trustees renames West Union after Brodhead, elects new chair</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/d8170386-a4cc-4f9b-910d-7929c85f7848.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Jack&#x20;Bovender,&#x20;Jr.,&#x20;chair&#x20;of&#x20;the&amp;nbsp&#x3B;Board&#x20;of&#x20;Trustees.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Jack Bovender, Jr., chair of the&nbsp;Board of Trustees.</p>

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/staff-reports">Staff Reports</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">May 13, 2017 | 1:25pm EDT</span>
                                </div>
                            </aside>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6 text-left text-md-right d-print-none">
                            <ul class="social-links list-unsyled list-inline mt-4 mt-md-0">
                                <li class="list-inline-item"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2017/05/board-of-trustees-renames-west-union-after-brodhead-elects-new-chair" target="_blank" class="sends-events" data-ga-category="Share" data-ga-action="click" data-ga-label="facebook" data-ga-value="CURL"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a></li>
